
** Modifiers

  - m multiple line
  - s single line, '.' matches new line
  - i insensitive, A match a
  - x, xx
      permitting white space and comments
      xx >= 5.26, white space in [] classes also ignored
  - p ingored >= 5.20
  - a, d, l, u
    >= 5.14
  - n does not fill $1, $2
  
** Escapes

  \w	match a word
  \W	match a non-word
  \s	match a whitespace
  \S	match a non-whitespace
  \d	match a digit
  \D	match a non-digit
  \pP	match a named property
  \p{P}
  \pp	match non-P
  \X	match unicode "eXtended grapheme cluster"
  \1	backreference to capture group
  \g1	dito
  \g{1} dito
  \g{-1}  	backreference relative
  \g{name}	named backreference
  \k<name>	named backreference
  \K	Keep only the stuff left from \K in $& ($MATCH)
  \N	Any character but not "\n"
  \v	vertical whitespace
  \V	not vertical whitespace
  \h	horizontal whitespace
  \H	not horizontal whitespace
  \R	Linebreak (\r, \r\n, \n)
  
** Matches

  $& 	match
  $`	prematch
  $'	postmatch
  
** Backslash

   \000		octal
   \a		character alarm
   \b{}, \b	boundary, [] character backspace
   \cX		control-x
   \e		character escape
   \E		turn off \Q, \L, \U
   \f		formfeed
   \F		foldcase till \E
   \G		pos assertion
   \l		lower case next character
   \L		lower case till \E
   \n		new line
   \N{}		named unicode character
   \o{}		octal sequence
   \p{}, \pP	match any character with the given unicode property
   \P{}, \PP	match any character without the given unicode property
   \Q		disable pattern meta characters till \E
